itunes:summary: On this episode, Matt takes the V60 Polestar Engineered to the canyons, we talk about what makes electric steering good (or bad!), and answer questions about bad engine swaps, fast commuters, and which is the better buy: a JDM Land Cruiser or a used G wagon.
